Followings are the packages that i am using in my projects. 


Accounts-password : This package  for the authenticiation in our system such as for the login, signup , forgot etc

Reactive Method : This package  for sedning the aschronous request to server

Iron router : This package used for the routing

Froala Editor : This package for WYSWIYG editor

Email : This package is for sending an email . Email will be send with smtp settings

Payapl : Package used for the paypal payments

Stripe: Used for the stripe payments


